GLOBAL_SPINS.HOW_TO_PLAY.DEFINE_DES: Global Spins are 3 handed sit n gos with a hyper structure. At the start of each game, a random multiplier will be spun and you could be lucky enough to find yourself playing for anything up to 10,000x your buy in! These fast paced tournaments are quick to play and action packed - perfect for the action-junkie poker player!
GLOBAL_SPINS.HOW_TO_PLAY.PRIZE_POOL_DES: Each Global Spin has a varied prizepool ranging from $2 to over $500,000!
